---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import heater from "../img/heater_.png"
---
<li class="justify-start items-center gap-12 inline-flex py-8">
    <div class="grow shrink basis-0 flex-col justify-start items-start gap-8 inline-flex">
        <Image alt="" src={heater} width={700} height={400} layout="responsive" />
    </div>
    <div class="grow shrink basis-0 flex-col justify-start items-start gap-4 inline-flex">
      <div class="self-stretch justify-start items-baseline gap-2 inline-flex">
        <div class="grow shrink basis-0 h-6 px-1 justify-center items-center gap-2.5 flex">
          <div class="grow shrink basis-0 text-stone-700 text-xl font-bold font-['Exo 2'] leading-normal tracking-wider">Compact (C)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="px-0.5 py-0.5 bg-white rounded-3xl justify-center items-center gap-0.5 flex">
          <div class="w-3.5 h-3.5 relative border border-white"></div>
          <div class="text-stone-700 text-xs font-normal font-['Exo 2'] leading-3 tracking-wide">Боковое подключение</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="self-stretch h-44 px-1 flex-col justify-start items-start gap-4 flex">
        <div class="justify-start items-center gap-4 inline-flex">
          <div class="text-stone-700 text-base font-bold font-['Exo 2'] leading-tight tracking-wider">Типы: 
          </div>
          <div class="justify-start items-center gap-2 flex">
            <div class="p-0.5 rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 text-center text-stone-200 text-sm font-extrabold font-['Exo 2'] leading-none tracking-wide">10</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-0.5 bg-[#fbd47e] rounded-3xl flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 text-center text-stone-600 text-sm font-extrabold font-['Exo 2'] leading-none tracking-wide">11</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-0.5 rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 text-center text-stone-200 text-sm font-extrabold font-['Exo 2'] leading-none tracking-wide">20</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-0.5 bg-[#fbd47e] rounded-3xl flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 text-center text-stone-600 text-sm font-extrabold font-['Exo 2'] leading-none tracking-wide">21</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-0.5 bg-[#fbd47e] rounded-3xl flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 text-center text-stone-600 text-sm font-extrabold font-['Exo 2'] leading-none tracking-wide">22</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-0.5 rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 text-center text-stone-200 text-sm font-extrabold font-['Exo 2'] leading-none tracking-wide">30</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-0.5 bg-[#fbd47e] rounded-3xl flex-col justify-center items-center gap-2.5 inline-flex">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 text-center text-stone-600 text-sm font-extrabold font-['Exo 2'] leading-none tracking-wide">33</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="self-stretch text-stone-700 text-sm font-normal font-['Exo 2'] leading-tight tracking-wide">Панельные радиаторы с боковым подключением широкого применения
        <br/>с конвекционными пластинами, боковыми защитными панелями и защитной решеткой сверху. Имеют четыре боковых присоединительных отверстия в каждом углу радиатора с внутренней резьбой G1/2. </div>
      </div>
      <div class="px-4 py-1 bg-[#fcd47f] rounded-2xl shadow justify-center items-center gap-3.5 inline-flex">
        <div class="text-center text-stone-700 text-base font-light font-['Exo 2'] leading-normal tracking-wider">Технические данные</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </li>